**  ER (ERROR MESSAGE)
E-01 BE SURE TO REMOVE THE KANBAN AND BE SURE TO READ AGAIN.
E-02 BE SURE TO READ THE KANBAN.
E-03 READING ERROR.
E-04 SUPPLIER ERROR.
E-05 THE INPUT DATA ISN'T FOUND TO RG CODE M/F NOT FOUND.
E-06 STOP KANBAN.
E-07 OFF THE SUBJECT.
E-08 INPUT (Y).
E-09 THE INPUT DATA ISN'T FOUND TO SORT CONDITION M/F.
E-10 REPETITION ERROR.
E-11 POCKET OVER.
E-12 INPUT (A OR B OR C).
E-13 RECEIVING ERROR.
E-14 CUSTOMER ERROR.
E-15 FACTORY ERROR.
E-16 THE INPUT DATA ISN'T FOUND TO TPX CUSTOMER M/F.
**  OP (OPERATION MESSAGE)
(Y) Y= I REMOVE KANBAN, AND LET YOU READ IT ONCE AGAIN.
TRAVELING ERROR OCCUR OF KANBAN. CHECK TRAVELING DEPARTMENT.
LEADER JAM OCCUR. CHECK LEADER DEPARTMENT.
KANBAN TWO CHANGING CHORUS OCCUR. CHECK LEADER DEPARTMENT.
